flowchart TD
    A[GET /features] --> B[List git worktrees]
    A --> C[List unmerged branches]

    B --> D[Filter: has specs/active/slug/]
    D --> E[Build FeatureInfo\nsourceType: worktree]

    C --> F[git branch --no-merged main]
    F --> G[Skip main/master/HEAD]
    G --> H[Derive slug from branch name]
    H --> I{Slug matches\nexisting worktree?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Skip - already covered]
    I -->|No| K[Check .review/sessions/slug-code.json]
    K --> L[Build FeatureInfo\nsourceType: branch]

    E --> M[Merge all features]
    L --> M
    M --> N[Return JSON response]

    style E fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#3b82f6
    style L fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#3b82f6
    style J fill:#3b1e1e,stroke:#ef4444
